{"name":"Damage Roll","type":"script","scope":"global","author":"E027q2TyDPSdEikA","img":"icons/svg/dice-target.svg","command":"/***************************************************************\n *\n * This macro can be used to trigger damage rolls.\n *\n * When a GM uses this macro, the damage roll dialog will be\n * generic if they have no tokens selected.  Otherwise the\n * damage roll will use the selected token's Actor data.\n *\n * When a player uses this macro, the skill check is tied to\n * the Actor that they own and control.\n *\n * @param {string} [weaponName] Name of the Weapon to use\n *                              (optional)\n *\n * @example\n * game.mc3e.macros.damageRoll();\n *\n * @example\n * game.mc3e.macros.damageRoll(\"Cutlass\");\n *\n * NOTE: If an weaponName is specified, this item must be owned\n * by the Actor selected, or if no Actor is selected it must\n * exist within the World.\n *\n * Reloads can only be used if both an Actor is selected and\n * the Weapon is ranged.\n *\n * When an item is specified, the Combat Dice value specified\n * on the Weapon is pre-populated in the Combat Dice box and\n * cannot be modified.  Additional dice required in this case\n * must be added using the \"Other\" box.\n **************************************************************/\n\ngame.mc3e.macros.damageRoll();","ownership":{"default":0,"E027q2TyDPSdEikA":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Macro.mYTMUl0HH7sj2PDv"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"mc3e","systemVersion":"1.7.1","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1672241152225,"modifiedTime":1672242343096,"lastModifiedBy":"E027q2TyDPSdEikA"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_id":"1McAbFO2lCxQLIH9"}
{"name":"Initialize Game","type":"script","scope":"global","author":"E027q2TyDPSdEikA","img":"systems/mc3e/assets/icons/macros/init-game.svg","command":"// This macro can be used to perform the following housekeeping\n// tasks at the start of a game:\n//\n//  - Reset every player character's Vigor, Resolve and Fortune to\n//    their maximum/starting values\n//  - Clears any left over personal momentum for every player\n//    character\n//  - Sets the player's shared Momentum pool to zero\n//  - Sets the Doom pool to the sum of all players' starting Fortune\n//\n// NOTE: Only users with the Game Master user role can run this macro\n//\ngame.mc3e.macros.initGame();","flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Macro.zeXFZ8kgJngt32nO"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"mc3e","systemVersion":"1.7.1","coreVersion":"10.288","createdTime":1667339420697,"modifiedTime":1667341283522,"lastModifiedBy":"E027q2TyDPSdEikA"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"E027q2TyDPSdEikA":3},"_id":"OfZjp1HGvXaoKWpD"}
{"name":"New Scene","type":"script","author":"E027q2TyDPSdEikA","img":"systems/mc3e/assets/icons/macros/new-scene.svg","scope":"global","command":"// This macro can be used to perform the following housekeeping\n// tasks when you want to start a new scene:\n//\n//  - Reset every player character's Vigor and Resolve to their\n//    current maximum.\n//  - Clears any left over personal momentum for every player\n//  - character\n//  - Reduces the players' shared Momentum pool by one\n//\n// NOTE: Only users with the Game Master user role can run this macro\n//\ngame.mc3e.macros.newScene();","flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Macro.NnyTToYprxCVW0h3"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"mc3e","systemVersion":"1.7.1","coreVersion":"10.288","createdTime":1667338689968,"modifiedTime":1667341281581,"lastModifiedBy":"E027q2TyDPSdEikA"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"E027q2TyDPSdEikA":3},"_id":"lMz5dxVFHDyGQVS6"}
{"name":"Basic Skill Roll","type":"script","scope":"global","author":"E027q2TyDPSdEikA","img":"icons/svg/dice-target.svg","command":"/***************************************************************\n * This macro can be used to roll a basic skill check that does\n * not have to be tied to a specific Actor.\n *\n * It displays a simplified interface to the normal skill roll\n * dialogue and does not automatically adjust Fortune, Doom\n * and Momentum pools.\n **************************************************************/\n\ngame.mc3e.macros.basicSkillRoll();","ownership":{"default":0,"E027q2TyDPSdEikA":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Macro.SIFvKTOHaTXka0Lj"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"mc3e","systemVersion":"1.7.1","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1672237305519,"modifiedTime":1672317247222,"lastModifiedBy":"E027q2TyDPSdEikA"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_id":"hauJjwyyYMCh6Ib6"}
{"name":"Combat Dice Roll","type":"script","scope":"global","author":"E027q2TyDPSdEikA","img":"icons/svg/dice-target.svg","command":"/***************************************************************\n * This macro can be used to roll an arbitrary amount of combat\n * dice.\n *\n * This version of the combat dice roller is designed for\n * ad-hoc rolls.\n **************************************************************/\n\ngame.mc3e.macros.combatDiceRoll();","ownership":{"default":0,"E027q2TyDPSdEikA":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Macro.yJIeFErOP5mys1lN"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"mc3e","systemVersion":"1.7.1","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1672237487596,"modifiedTime":1672317251802,"lastModifiedBy":"E027q2TyDPSdEikA"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_id":"4WLouIhS4q2clIsX"}
{"name":"Cover Soak Roll","type":"script","scope":"global","author":"E027q2TyDPSdEikA","img":"icons/svg/dice-target.svg","command":"/***************************************************************\n * This macro can be used to roll an arbitrary amount of combat\n * dice for a cover check and includes selectable presets\n * supported by the core rules.\n *\n * @param {string} [itemName] Name of the item being used for\n *                            the Soak roll.\n *\n * @param {number} [soak]     The amount of Combat Dice of Soak\n *                            provided by the item.\n *\n * @example\n * game.mc3e.macros.coverSoakDiceRoll();\n *\n * @example\n * game.mc3e.macros.coverSoakDiceRoll(\"Big Shield\", 3);\n *\n * NOTE: This macro is basically a wrapper around the\n * soakDiceRoll macro.\n **************************************************************/\n\ngame.mc3e.macros.coverSoakDiceRoll(\"Lump of Wood\", 7);","ownership":{"default":0,"E027q2TyDPSdEikA":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Macro.pQlnAF51HhigN1j0"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"mc3e","systemVersion":"1.7.1","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1672237597669,"modifiedTime":1672317260093,"lastModifiedBy":"E027q2TyDPSdEikA"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_id":"gVslgHYZJLTlQh1R"}
